向本院提出抗告狀。\r\n                              書記官    卓采薇\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　7 　　月　　26　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e5%96%ae%e7%a6%81%e6%b2%92%2c292%2c20220725%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,單禁沒,292,20220725,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"單禁沒","JNO":"292","JDATE":"20220725","JTITLE":"宣告沒收"}